安装：
curl -sSL https://get.docker.com/
sh install.sh


http://tuxknight-notes.readthedocs.org/en/latest/index.html


修改docker远程访问权限"

sudo gedit /etc/default/docker

添加：
DOCKER_OPTS="-H=unix:///var/run/docker.sock -H=0.0.0.0:6732"  


docker remote api
https://github.com/docker/docker/blob/master/docs/reference/api/docker_remote_api_v1.22.md
